  "meal_prep_notes": "The batter keeps 2 days in the fridge and thickens slightly; loosen with 1 to 2 tbsp water before cooking again. Cooked adai reheat well in an airless skillet over low heat for 90 seconds per side. Batch-cook and cool fully before stacking between parchment.",
